\left(a^{x}-1\right)\log b+\left(a^{y}-1\right)\log c+\left(a^{z}-1\right)\log d\geq\log a\left(x\log b+y\log c+z\log d\right).
\geq\log a\left((x+y)\log c+z\log d\right).
